QuestData.Title: Results: Inconclusive
QuestData.Description: I did all I could, $n. I had the right potions... I had the right recipes... but the source of this sample eludes me. It's tens of thousands of years old, but we've shown that it's not of titan origin. And it's not saronite, I can tell you just by looking at it. So... what in Brann's name is it?$b$bTell Bronwyn that I tried my best. Sorry.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Opened Mosh'Ogg Bounty to Bronwyn at the Explorers' League Camp in the Cape of Stranglethorn.
QuestData.RewardText: I knew that alchemist was all talk. Well, thanks for your help, $n. I know you tried.
